Products.RichDescription:
Bite sized bickies packed with multi-coloured choc chips!

Paradise Uglies are great to share with friends or as a special treat and are a lot of fun to hand out at parties. They're also great as a lunchbox or after school snack.

Paradise Uglies meet the gang

Dr. Bionic

Once a respectable citizen and leading scientist in his day, Dr. bionic joined the force of evil when one of his experiments went drastically wrong, frying his brain and sending him 'mad'. Now, he spends night and day working on a special cookie that when eaten will turn all the children into his loyal slaves.

Spike

Spike has been living in the monster's lair since he was abandoned in the woods and taken in by Dr. bionic. He's not the brightest dinosaur and is always getting in trouble when his clumsiness interferes with the professor's experiments. Although he looks tough he scares easily and has a tendency to hide under his bed during thunderstorms.

Stinkie

So named because he is trying to set a new record for not washing. Stinkie is extremely messy, has poor manners, and loves nothing more than a good food fight. He is mischievous and hyperactive, always looking for excitement and never able to sit still.

Arlo

Humble servant to Dr. bionic, arlo is loyal and obedient, with a vocabulary that includes only the words 'yes master'. Many years ago, lonely and without work, he was taken in by Dr. bionic, and appointed caretaker of the house, a job which he takes great pride in.
